{"tid":1519431,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"(689式抵制TVB)洗版俾嬲罷買三大行動，缺一不可","createTime":"2019-08-30T14:38:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-05T14:45:46.000Z","uid":75759,"like":61,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"cbff66aab0d28ebf67496155f75540eae809c512","tid":1519431,"uid":75759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T14:38:17.000Z","msg":"<strong>連登689黃心穎表示，相關人士在樓豬作出警告後仍落TVB廣告，應自己評估風險。<br />\n<br />\n他重申，樓豬作出警告前，已有足夠時間讓相關人士撤回。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n是日主要目標(30/8)：<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">Expedia</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/paNh8qq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpaNh8qq.jpg&h=a3f79381&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/expedia.com.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fexpedia.com.hk%2F&d=7hybd32tUfzicQL4e%2Fav0spe%2FvQB%2B59L3xQItPRvby0%3D&h=65f6520c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/expedia.com.hk/</a><br />\n盡管<span style=\"color: red;\">2個多月以嚟大量市民要求Expedia撤回CCTVB廣告，但Expedia卻完全無作出回應，比林鄭更差更冷漠</span>。在此呼籲市民及其親戚朋友保持初心，永不使用Expedia，轉用其他媒介訂酒店。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>Expedia特製留言template</strong><br />\n1️⃣ Expedia漠視市民訴求，已呼籲朋友永遠停止使用！貴公司有權選擇其他廣告公司，正如大眾同樣有權選擇你的競爭對手！<br />\n<br />\n2️⃣ 我本身好支持你哋公司架，但係多次呼籲你地唔好再落TVB廣告都唔聽，有無搞錯。已經叫曬身邊所有人以後唔再幫襯Expedia！如果廣告部或者廣告公司hard sell 你買TVB，請考慮換咗廣告部同事或廣告公司！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n是日匪趣台廣告排行榜(1.5小時內)<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Hipp喜寶</span> 4次，<span style=\"color: red;\">三度衛冕榜首</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">御藥堂</span> 3次，<span style=\"color: red;\">共2分鐘</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">維特健靈</span> 2次，<span style=\"color: red;\">共2分鐘</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">舒適達</span> 2次<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Scalp X防掉髮</span> 2次<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Happycall廚具</span> 2次<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">海馬牌床褥</span> 2次<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">美贊臣奶粉</span> 2次<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">大棧</span> 2次<br />\n<br />\n其中<span style=\"color: red;\">舒適達</span>、<span style=\"color: red;\">Happycall廚具</span>、<span style=\"color: red;\">美贊臣奶粉</span>算係唔係target廢老而我哋未集中洗版嘅品牌，當中以<span style=\"color: red;\">舒適達</span>廣告嘅Airtime最長，優先考慮。<br />\n<br />\n是日洗版精選推介，排名分先後分別為<br />\n1. <span style=\"color: gold;\">舒適達</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://zh-hk.facebook.com/SensodyneHK/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh-hk.facebook.com%2FSensodyneHK%2F&d=7hybd32tUfzicQL4e%2Fav0spe%2FvQB%2B59L3xQItPRvby0%3D&h=482dc7ea\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh-hk.facebook.com/SensodyneHK/</a><br />\n2. <span style=\"color: gold;\">美贊臣</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/meadjohnsonhk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fmeadjohnsonhk%2F&d=7hybd32tUfzicQL4e%2Fav0spe%2FvQB%2B59L3xQItPRvby0%3D&h=a292aa5e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/meadjohnsonhk/</a><br />\n3. <span style=\"color: gold;\">Happycall</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/happycallhk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhappycallhk%2F&d=7hybd32tUfzicQL4e%2Fav0spe%2FvQB%2B59L3xQItPRvby0%3D&h=0d2bb6b4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/happycallhk/</a><br />\n<br />\n通用留言template<br />\n二選一，亦歡迎巴絲發揮創意<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n1️⃣ 無綫新聞，助紂為虐，恥與為伍，撤回廣告！希望貴公司重新檢視你所僱用之廣告公司及其廣告計劃。貴公司有權選擇其他廣告公司，正如大眾同樣有權選擇你的競爭對手！<br />\n<br />\n2️⃣ 我本身好支持你哋公司嘅產品，奈何本人對貴公司於賣港媒體TVB落廣告此舉極為反感，決定罷買產品直至見唔到TVB 廣告為止。如果廣告部或者廣告公司hard sell 你買TVB，請考慮換咗廣告部同事或廣告公司！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">藍絲專用留言</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n看到贵公司在黄丝传媒CCTVB打广告，本人以及亲友们决定不会再支持贵公司<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">恥與為伍每日任務</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/husky/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n1. 洗版<img src=\"/assets/faces/husky/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2. 俾嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n3. 罷買<img src=\"/assets/faces/husky/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong>你今日做咗未！？(3/3)</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/husky/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>我呼籲各位連登手足每晚10點叫完口號都入黎幫手㩒兩個制洗版，<span style=\"color: red;\">如果唔係廣告界手足想幫口勸退廣告商都無牙力呀</span>！全民抵制TVB，要佢做第二個亞視！</strong>"},{"pid":"f5dcda0b939c3129006fae8acac52abefd98442d","tid":1519431,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T14:38:36.000Z","msg":"幾句講哂<br />\n831宗教集會<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">901 1點鐘 機場見</span></span><br />\n92大三罷<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OvNBCkd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOvNBCkd.jpg&h=f0ee9ddd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">記住啊 我地只係幫機管局做交通壓力測試</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">901 機場 Channel</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" da